<h1>Student#index</h1>

<p><h3>Hello, Tutors! Below, you'll find a list of students needing help.</br>
If you can help them, please hit the SCHEDULE LESSON button next to their name, and </br>
fill out the necessary info to schedule a time to meet. Thanks!</h3></p>

<h2>STUDENTS:</h2>

<% @students.each do |s| %>
    <ul>
    <li><%= s.first_name %> <%= s.last_name[0] %>.
    is in <%= s.grade %>th grade, and needs help in <%= s.subject_help %>,
    specifically: "<%= s.student_bio %></br>
    <%= link_to "Schedule Lesson", new_lesson_path(s) %>
    </li>
    </ul>
    <% end %>